sub_title: Anderwoud: translation done well, only better.
summary:
Starting out as a humble marketing translator and specializing in retail (fashion, automotive, animal supplies, travel, insurance) and a couple of cookbooks on the side, I am currently translating adult romance/erotica. I know what's on offer and think the majority of what is published lacks quality. I focus on well-written stories and deliver high quality texts, going the extra mile for the reader. Do you?

Strengths and specialties: 

+ translation, copywriting and blogging
+ multilingual (Dutch, English, Swedish, plus knowledge of French and German) 
+ organizational talent with eye for improvement
+ very high standards
+ approachable personality
